<!-- ============================================================================
     InDows module: autologon
     Signs the account in automatically at boot, without typing the password. Pairs with the
     'username' module (same account).

     WHERE: settings pass="oobeSystem" > component "Microsoft-Windows-Shell-Setup"
     ANCHOR (a comment in the base) named:   [InDows:module] account

     REPLACE: __USERNAME__ (the account) and __PASSWORD__ (its password; empty value if no password).
     PERMANENT auto-logon as written. For a ONE-TIME auto-logon, add <LogonCount>1</LogonCount>.

     SECURITY: the password is stored in CLEAR TEXT in autounattend.xml. Never commit a real password
     to a public repo. Auto-logon also means anyone who powers on the PC is logged in as you.
     ============================================================================ -->
<AutoLogon>
    <Username>__USERNAME__</Username>
    <Enabled>true</Enabled>
    <Password>
        <Value>__PASSWORD__</Value>
        <PlainText>true</PlainText>
    </Password>
</AutoLogon>
